      "created_at": "2016-05-30 16:01:19 UTC",
      "updated_at": "2016-05-30 16:01:19 UTC",
      "body": "I suppose the wording in that sections could be better. scalafmt is quite opinionated on how argument/parameter lists look like so it may create larger diffs than scalariform. Still, it shouldn't create larger diffs than opinionated formatters for other languages such as dartfmt and clang-format."
